  <body>
    <sec>
      <title>Results</title>
      <p>Consistent with earlier findings <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="B1">1</xref>, metformin reduced fasting glucose in adults with prediabetes. In contrast to an earlier report <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="B3">3</xref>, the effect persisted and remained significant at twelve months.</p>
    </sec>
    <sec>
      <title>Discussion</title>
      <p>The assay protocol was performed as described previously <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="B2">2</xref>. Overall, metformin decreased fasting glucose in this cohort.</p>
    </sec>
  </body>
